1. *Kod* nas doma ima puno mačaka. (At our house, there are a lot of cats.)
2. Doktor je rekao da će se *kod* njega javiti za nekoliko dana. (The doctor said that he will come back in a few days.)
3. Škola će biti zatvorena *kod* oblačnog vremena. (The school will be closed in case of bad weather.)
4. *Kod* većine dece, grip traje nekoliko dana. (In most cases, the flu lasts a few days.)
5. Ona je imala veliku prednost *kod* zadatka. (She had a big advantage with the task.)